  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName' id='Alis_Core_Graphic_OpenGL_Enums_TextureParameterName'>Enum TextureParameterName    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Graphic/src/OpenGL/Enums/TextureParameterName.cs#L35'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.html'>Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture parameter name enum</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum TextureParameterName</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>TextureBaseLevel = 33084</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture base level texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureBorderColor = 4100</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture border color texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureCompareMode = 34892</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture compare mode texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureCompareFunc = 34893</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture compare func texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureLodBias = 34049</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture lod bias texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureMagFilter = 10240</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture mag filter texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureMaxLevel = 33085</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture max level texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureMaxLod = 33083</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture max lod texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureMinFilter = 10241</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture min filter texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureMinLod = 33082</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture min lod texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureSwizzleR = 36418</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture swizzle texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureSwizzleG = 36419</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture swizzle texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureSwizzleB = 36420</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture swizzle texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureSwizzleA = 36421</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture swizzle texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureSwizzleRgba = 36422</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture swizzle rgba texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureWrapS = 10242</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture wrap texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureWrapT = 10243</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture wrap texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TextureWrapR = 32882</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The texture wrap texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>MaxAnisotropyExt = 34046</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.TextureParameterName.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The max anisotropy ext texture parameter name</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
